<section class="founder">
  <div class="founder__text">
    <h2 class="founder__text--mainHeading section__heading">Nashe Dan 
      <span class="founder__text--subHeading">/ Founder</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="founder__text--paragraph">"Hi. I'm a highschool dropout who quite like you, is living in a world of perspectives defined by celebrated scholarly naivete. I've grown to understand that in most rooms, this fact speaks loads against me but I don't mind though.
    The loudest boos often come from the nosebleeds. If you are positive and daring in your pursuit of right, please hang
    around. You may have found a friend in me. Oh and hi again, <a href="/projects">I'm Dan!</a> üôãüèΩ."</p>

    <p class="founder__text--paragraph">
      Although the text above is an excerpt from <a href="/projects">my story</a>, all OUR human experiences speak to a broader and
      universal picture.
      That of resilience and belief in oneself and in the deeper sense of 'family' embedded in our social constructs or
      maybe... the lack of it sometimes!
    </p>

    <p class="founder__text--paragraph">While I still draw great inspiration from the stories my hidden scars tell, it took me a fair bit of time to realize it takes courage to admit that we all need help sometimes.
      That is why I created urAfro. To make positive change and to make it together.
    </p>

    <p class="italic founder__text--paragraph">Let's live for <span class="brand">We</span> &nbsp; 'N feel good while <span class="brand">doing it.</span></p>
  </div>
  <div class="founder__image">
    <!-- link will diret user to founder page (ABOUT ME PAGE?) -->
    <a href="https://github.com/tinashy" target="_blank" class="btn btn-full caveat">
      about Foundr
